OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FAfter
OL,6,Fchilly start, Friday will be dry for
OL,7,Fmany, but showers are possible, these
OL,8,Flocally heavy on Friday. Longer
OL,9,Fperiods of rain are possible on
OL,10,FSaturday and Sunday. Turning warmer.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
